---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../../consts";
---

<Layout title={`Shopify Development | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Professional Shopify development services for your e-commerce business">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Shopify Development</h1>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg">
        We create custom Shopify stores that are beautiful, functional, and optimized for conversions. Our experienced developers combine technical
        expertise with creative design to deliver Shopify solutions that drive business growth.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Overview -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Expert Shopify Development Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          At Company X, we specialize in creating custom Shopify stores that are tailored to your unique business needs. Whether you're launching a
          new brand or upgrading an existing store, our team of certified Shopify experts can help you build a powerful online presence.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We take a strategic approach to Shopify development, focusing on user experience, conversion optimization, and scalability. Our solutions
          are designed to grow with your business and adapt to changing market demands.
        </p>
        <p>
          With our deep understanding of the Shopify platform and e-commerce best practices, we deliver stores that not only look great but also
          perform exceptionally well in terms of speed, functionality, and sales performance.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Shopify Development" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Our Services -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Our Shopify Development Services</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Service 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Custom Store Development</h3>
          <p>
            We build custom Shopify stores that stand out from templates and reflect your brand identity. Our developers create unique shopping
            experiences that engage customers and drive conversions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Theme Customization</h3>
          <p>
            We customize Shopify themes to match your brand aesthetic and business requirements. Our experts can transform standard themes into unique
            storefronts with custom features and functionality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Custom App Development</h3>
          <p>
            We develop custom Shopify apps that extend your store's functionality and help you solve unique business challenges. Our custom apps
            integrate seamlessly with your Shopify store.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 10h18M3 14h18m-9-4v8m-7 0h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Shopify Plus Development</h3>
          <p>
            For enterprise clients, we offer specialized Shopify Plus development services, leveraging the platform's advanced features for
            high-volume merchants.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Third-party Integrations</h3>
          <p>
            We seamlessly integrate your Shopify store with third-party services and tools, including payment gateways, shipping solutions, CRM
            systems, and marketing platforms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Performance Optimization</h3>
          <p>
            We optimize your Shopify store for speed, performance, and search engines. Our optimization services ensure your store loads quickly and
            ranks well in search results.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Choose Us -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Why Choose Us for Shopify Development</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Certified Shopify Experts</h3>
            <p>Our team consists of certified Shopify experts with years of experience building successful e-commerce stores.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">End-to-End Solutions</h3>
            <p>We offer complete solutions from store setup and design to ongoing maintenance and optimization.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Conversion-Focused Approach</h3>
            <p>We design and develop with conversion in mind, focusing on user experience that drives sales.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Ongoing Support</h3>
            <p>We don't disappear after launch. Our team provides continuous support and maintenance for your Shopify store.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Recent Projects -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Recent Shopify Projects</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Project 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Luxury Fashion Store" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Luxury Fashion Store</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Custom Shopify store for a high-end fashion retailer with advanced filtering and personalized shopping experiences.
            </p>
            <a href="/case-studies/luxury-fashion-boutique" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">View Case Study →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Organic Food Marketplace" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Organic Food Marketplace</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Multi-vendor marketplace for organic food products with inventory management and delivery scheduling.</p>
            <a href="/case-studies/organic-food-marketplace" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">View Case Study →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Handcrafted Jewelry Brand" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Handcrafted Jewelry Brand</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Custom Shopify store with product customization features and seamless checkout experience.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">View Case Study →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Create Your Custom Shopify Store?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Contact us today to discuss your Shopify development project. Our experts will help you create a store that reflects your brand and drives
        business growth.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-100 transition">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

